    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs beautifully, and has been super well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve kept up with it well, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
