    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension geometry that maintains its signature communicative steering. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing inspection. While it displays the honest character of a well-enjoyed performance machine, its powertrain synchronization and lateral dynamics remain remarkably sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
