    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for, reliable daily driver. The exterior showcases a vibrant, deep-gloss finish that has been regularly waxed, with only minor road-wear consistent with its age. Inside, the interior remains remarkably clean; the leather seats show light, natural creasing but are free of any cracks or tears, and the dashboard remains pristine. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, navigation, and heated seats, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule and recent fluid changes. It drives straight and true, with responsive handling and a quiet, comfortable cabin. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer its next owner. Includes two sets of keys and a full folder of service records.",
